<tr><td>
<font class="hint">
You will have the opportunity to enter a unique price and/or discount for each product that will affect the base price 
(but not options) - if you leave this field blank then the base price will be used.<br>
</font>

<br>

<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_DISCOUNT_DEFAULT --> name="chk_discount_default"> Default Pricing Formula: <input type="textbox" size="20" value="<!-- DISCOUNT_AMOUNT -->" name="discount_amount"> (only used if no unique formula is set)<br>

<!-- FORMULA_ERROR -->

<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_INCOMPLETE --> name="chk_incomplete"> Ignore/Disable Special pricing for incomplete items.<br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_REWARDS --> name="chk_rewards"> Allow participation in rewards program. (**)<br>
<br>
<u>Promotions:</u><br>
<input type="radio" <!-- PROMOTION_MODE_0 --> name="promotion_mode" value="0"> Disable Promotions<br>
<input type="radio" <!-- PROMOTION_MODE_1 --> name="promotion_mode" value="1"> Use default store promotions. (RECOMMENDED)<br>
<div class="hint">
HINT: Promotions can selectively have different behaviors per schedule, based on the the rules logic within them.
</div>
<div class="hint">
REMINDER: Promotions and Coupons are DIFFERENT. If you do not want a coupon to be enabled for one or more wholesale 
schedules you must Disable each coupon individually.
</div>
<br>
<u>Shipping:</u><br>
<input type="radio" <!-- SHIPRULE_MODE_0 --> name="shiprule_mode" value="0"> Disable/Skip all shipping rules.<br>
<input type="radio" <!-- SHIPRULE_MODE_1 --> name="shiprule_mode" value="1"> Apply rules based on how they are configured. (RECOMMENDED)<br>
<font size='1'>NOTE: You can configure shipping rules so they only apply to certain schedules.</font><br>
<br>
<u>Customer Access</u><br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_REALTIME_ORDERS --> name="chk_realtime_orders"> Accept EDI/XML Orders from customers. (**)<br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_REALTIME_PRODUCTS --> name="chk_realtime_products"> Give customers EDI/XML product download access. (*)<br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_REALTIME_INVENTORY --> name="chk_realtime_inventory"> Give customers EDI/XML inventory download access. (**)<br>

<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_DROPSHIP_INVOICE --> name="chk_dropship_invoice"> Allow customers to provide their own packing slip/invoice and logo information for dropship orders (*).<br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_EXPORT_INVENTORY --> name="chk_export_inventory"> Allow customers to export/print out a complete inventory list. (*)<br>
<input type="checkbox" <!-- CHK_INVENTORY_IGNORE --> name="chk_inventory_ignore"> Ignore Inventory: Allow customers to purchase unlimited quantities. (**)<br>
<BR>
<u>Internationalization</u><br>
