<div class="hint">
* This feature allows you to specify an alternate price list in another currency.
Requires level 8 account or higher.
Not compatible with pricing formulas, fixed price promotions, or option based price
modifiers.  We recommend naming these schedules CXXX where XXX is the currency code.
for example CEUR ("currency euro") or "CCAD" (currency canadian dollars).
</div>

